author: maxb
msg: Switch svn2rss.py from pickle to cPickle, and remove needless use of StringIO,
bringing a noteworth speed-up (~30% faster when generating many items).
(Svn2RSS.pickle): Stop needlessly using a StringIO object.

author: rooneg
msg: Follow up to r20717, make the fixes to the pool destruction ordering bug
(clear_cache): This.  Also clear out the cache in addition to the lock.
(svn_fs_bdb__close): Check for bdb_cache being NULL, not bdb_cache_lock,
since bdb_cache_lock is not defined if APR_HAS_THREADS is 0.
